  <title>GLib.OptionContext.prototype.set_help_enabled</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function set_help_enabled(help_enabled: Boolean): void {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_option_context_set_help_enabled()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Enables or disables automatic generation of `--help` output.
By default, <link xref="GLib.OptionContext.parse"/> recognizes `--help`, `-h`,
`-?`, `--help-all` and `--help-groupname` and creates suitable
output to stdout.</p>
  <p>Since 2.6</p>
<terms>
<item>
<title><code>help_enabled</code></title>
  <p><code>true</code> to enable `--help`, <code>false</code> to disable it</p>
</item>
